name: Dada Life
description: '''Dada Life''' are a [[Swedish people|Swedish]] [[DJ]] duo formed in 2006, which consists of [[Olle Corn√©er]] and Stefan Engblom. They have released three albums, a number of singles and remixes and one compilation. The duo had early chart success in Belgium and the Netherlands, while their second album ''The Rules of Dada'' reached the ''Billboard'' 200. They are known for their humour during their live performances, while their name is a homage to the [[Dada|absurdist movement]] of the early twentieth century. They have released multiple audio plugins programmed by Tailored Noise: Endless Smile, Space In-Your-Face, Wide Awake, Eternal Return and most notably Sausage Fattener, a saturator.
